=Description=

"The Community Lover’s Guide to the Universe is a growing collection of stories and book editions, bringing together the experiences of many amazing people and their innovative projects - people who are actively and creatively making community, together.
​​
​
Each book is produced collaboratively, and focuses on a particular place or theme. The website is a wider collection of stories, blog posts and reflective essays on this emergent new community culture.
﻿
The aim of the Community Lover’s Guide is to surface and share this new community practice widely."
(http://www.communityloversguide.org/)


